Bot-BasicBot-Pluggable-Module-Crontab
=====================================

This module implements a crontab-like feature to send messages to a nominated
IRC channel at specific periods in time.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Bot::BasicBot::Pluggable
    IO::File


